body_html:
@shakith Thanks for the detailed description of the problem. Can you please say how you added all obj files to solution?

I saw list of .obj files needed to build tf_label_image_example in solution explorer and was amazed how big it is. Maybe some of them may be skipped (or added automatically)?

![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/9510143/21359502/84694102-c6ed-11e6-862b-03905aa74e98.png)

UPDATE:
@shakith Thank you very much! Tensorflow works fine after i added .obj files.

If somebody faced same issue:

I copied from tf_label_image_example.vcxproj these lines to custom.vcxproj: https://gist.github.com/derofim/fd461d42104567b4fc0cd687dec9f464

Note that <ClCompile Include="D:\Tensorflow\tensorflow-master\tensorflow\examples\label_image\main.cc" /> removed (I replaced main.cc with custom source code).

Also i created filter "Object Libraries" and copied from tf_label_image_example.vcxproj.filters these lines to custom.vcxproj.filters:
https://gist.github.com/derofim/9ba812c9234f50a6d5142c73fdc0f5cc

@shakith Thanks for the detailed description of the problem. Can you please say how you added all obj files to solution? 

```
I saw list of .obj files needed to build tf_label_image_example in solution explorer and was amazed how big it is. Maybe some of them may be skipped (or added automatically)?

![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/9510143/21359502/84694102-c6ed-11e6-862b-03905aa74e98.png)
```

**UPDATE**:
@shakith Thank you very much! Tensorflow works fine after i added .obj files.

If somebody faced same issue:

I copied from tf_label_image_example.vcxproj these lines to custom.vcxproj: https://gist.github.com/derofim/fd461d42104567b4fc0cd687dec9f464

Note that `<ClCompile Include="D:\Tensorflow\tensorflow-master\tensorflow\examples\label_image\main.cc"  />` removed (I replaced main.cc with custom source code).

Also i created filter "Object Libraries" and copied from tf_label_image_example.vcxproj.filters these lines to custom.vcxproj.filters:
https://gist.github.com/derofim/9ba812c9234f50a6d5142c73fdc0f5cc
